flowchart TD
  U[User or evaluator] --> API[FastAPI API routes]
  API --> ORCH[Agent orchestrator]

  ORCH --> RET[Retrieval subsystem]
  RET --> CHUNKS[Retrieved chunks]
  CHUNKS --> INJ[Injection detector]
  INJ --> CTX[Admitted or quarantined context]
  CTX --> ORCH

  ORCH --> POLICY[Security middleware]
  POLICY --> TOOLRISK[Tool-risk classifier]
  TOOLRISK --> TOOLS[Controlled tool registry]
  TOOLS --> OBS[Tool observations]
  OBS --> INJ

  ORCH --> RELEASE[Response release check]
  RELEASE --> EXFIL[Exfiltration detector]
  EXFIL --> RESP[Safe, sanitized, or blocked response]

  POLICY --> LOGS[Security decision log]
  INJ --> LOGS
  EXFIL --> LOGS

  subgraph Trust_Boundaries[Trust boundaries]
    INPUT[Input boundary]
    CONTEXT[Context boundary]
    ACTION[Action boundary]
    OUTPUT[Release boundary]
  end

  INPUT -.-> API
  CONTEXT -.-> INJ
  ACTION -.-> TOOLRISK
  OUTPUT -.-> EXFIL
